I’m proud that Truett Hurst Winery has become an industry leading innovator,retail exclusive brand developer, national brand supplierand direct to consumer provider.Our company has grown significantly from the ground up in late2007 to today and our world class team is poised to make better wines than ever beforewhile continuing to work with the country’s most important wine retailers.Please accept my personal invitation to visit our beautiful winery and tasting roomin the acclaimed Dry Creek Valley so we can share the hospitalitythat our customers have come to appreciate.

— Phillip L. Hurst, President, Chief Executive Officer and Director



















